    <bioghist>
      <head>Biographical Note</head>
      <p>Ruth Poindexter Brown was a resident of Franklin, Tennessee and died July 27, 2003. From 1970 to the spring of 1972 Brown attended the University of Oklahoma. In the fall of 1972 she was admitted as an undergraduate transfer student to Vanderbilt
        University.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
      <p>The contents within this collection are three folders of Vanderbilt brochures, documents and correspondence from Brown&#8217;s time as a student.</p>
    </scopecontent>
